  "description": "A sprawling panoramic view of a city nestled between rolling green hills and a distant body of water. The city is densely packed with buildings of varying heights, creating a textured urban landscape. A significant portion of the foreground is dominated by lush, green hillsides covered in trees and vegetation. The sky is overcast with gray clouds, casting a soft, diffused light over the entire scene. Some buildings are visible on the hillsides, blending into the landscape. The body of water in the distance appears calm and muted. There is a slight haze affecting visibility.",
